      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED HOT BERNIE (8) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Scored over 300m at this track last time in a Free For All (16.88). Form at the trip excellent including 12 wins. Boasts a strong record from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from six starts. Hard to go past. ELITE GENERAL (1) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at this track over 300m behind RED HOT BERNIE (17.34) in a Free For All. Was in the money prior to that. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. FEARLESS PARKER (2) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (17.07) in a Free For All at this track. Expected to do much better this time. DANCING DENNIS (4) placed out of the same box last time out - worth some thought.",
